<item>
            <title>[HBASE-538] Improve exceptions that come out on client-side</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/HBASE-538</link>
                <project id="12310753" key="HBASE">HBase</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Client-side exceptions should contain regionserver and region client was going against.  Looking at an UnknownScannerException that came out of a client, it looks like something happened over on the regionserver but my cluster has a 20-plus machines and I don&apos;t know which I should be looking at.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
